  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. This package evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. The intended use is pre-market submission support for a Class III implantable VAD; the model must demonstrate adequate credibility for predicting normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) within ±15% of in-vitro measurements across the clinical operating envelope (3–6 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM). Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed. All 13 credibility factors have been assessed; required levels are met or exceeded for each factor. Decision: Accepted.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/cfd-hemolysis-vad-class3-claim-001",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/fda-centrifugal-pump-cfd-v2",
